Revision history for Perl extension Brat::Handler.

0.11
     - when loading files from a directory, check if it is brat file (.ann extension)
     - add script for printing term list in a file or standard output
     - add script for printing relation list in a file or standard output
     - add functions for getting term list and relation list as array
     - for each script: several directories containing files to load can be specified
     - term id can start with TS (or T)
     - add functions for global statistics
     - add functions for getting term and relations types
     - add script for printing statistics
     - bug correction in the method loadFiles
0.1
     - Version of YaTeA with a CPAN configuration
